<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
       
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
       
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Başvuru Başarılı</title>
        <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-color: #0c1f4c;
            --success-color: #28a745;
            --secondary-color: #007bff;
            --bg-color: #f7f9fc;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 60px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            /* Daha yumuşak köşeler */
            box-shadow: 0 15px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Daha belirgin gölge */
            max-width: 480px;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--success-color);
            /* Yeşil vurgu çizgisi */
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Checkmark stilleri (Aynı kalır, animasyon için gereklidir) */
        .checkmark {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: block;
            stroke-width: 3;
            stroke: var(--success-color);
            stroke-miterlimit: 10;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px var(--success-color);
            animation: fill .4s ease-in-out .4s forwards, scale .3s ease-in-out .9s both;
        }

        .checkmark__circle {
            stroke-dasharray: 166;
            stroke-dashoffset: 166;
            stroke-width: 3;
            stroke-miterlimit: 10;
            stroke: var(--success-color);
            fill: none;
            animation: stroke 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.45, 1) forwards;
        }

        .checkmark__check {
            transform-origin: 50% 50%;
            stroke-dasharray: 48;
            stroke-dashoffset: 48;
            animation: stroke 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.45, 1) 0.8s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes stroke {
            100% {
                stroke-dashoffset: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes scale {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: none;
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale3d(1.1, 1.1, 1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fill {
            100% {
                box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 40px var(--success-color);
            }
        }

        /* Yeni Metin Stilleri */
        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            /* Daha kalın başlık */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Link Stilleri */
        .links a {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .links a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* Mobil ayarlamalar */
        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
        <div class="container">
                <svg class="checkmark" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 52 52">
                       
            <circle class="checkmark__circle" cx="26" cy="26" r="25" fill="none" />
                       
            <path class="checkmark__check" fill="none" d="M14.1 27.2l7.1 7.2 16.7-16.8" />
                   
        </svg>
                <h1>Başvurunuz Alındı!</h1>
                <p>Talebiniz başarıyla işlendi ve ilgili birimimize iletilmiştir. Değerlendirmeniz en kısa sürede
            yapılacaktır.</p>
                <div class="links">
                        <a href="/">Yeni Başvuru Yap</a>
                    </div>
            </div>
</body>

</html>